title: How to Insert SIM card of E5786S-62A？
answer:
A：Remove back cover using the thumb catch on the bottom of the device and gently lift off. 

![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=37524)


 To Insert the SIM card, slide in as shown with the chip facing down. Push the SIM card in until it clicks into place. 

 To remove SIM card, push in card until it clicks and pops out.
